just_use users.go

# label: WORKHORSE
# role: supports feature — user read endpoints + self-settings update

Handles /users, /users/{id}, /users/by_email, /users/me, and PATCH
/settings. Currently only full_name is settable; the endpoint is shaped to
grow additional fields without new routes. Self-update pushes realm_user
to every connected client so names update in real time.
